sentences.english: Field projects are implemented in all types of natural forests.
sentences.chinese: 各類天然林實地區項目得到落實。

sentences.english: Becoming a doctor requires years of training there are really no short cuts.
sentences.chinese: 當醫生需要多年的學習和鍛鍊實無捷徑可言。

sentences.english: The song was of great importance and benefits to Zhuge Liang's aspiration and achievement in life.
sentences.chinese: 此事於諸葛亮一生之志節與事業，裨益實多。

sentences.english: To write the true natural expression of emotions, can not be affected and moan and groan without being ill.
sentences.chinese: 要寫真實情感的自然流露，不可做作和無病呻吟。

sentences.english: Deeds are fruits, words are but leaver.
sentences.chinese: 行動時果實，言語只是葉子。

sentences.english: There is really no such thing as bad weather, only different kinds of good weather.
sentences.chinese: 世上實無惡劣天氣，只有好天氣的種種不同罷了。

sentences.english: However if the constraints are unsteady, a small real displacement is no longer a virtual one.
sentences.chinese: 而在非定常約束下，微小實位移不再是虛位移之一。

sentences.english: In fact, an abstract class gives you more flexibility when it comes to evolution.
sentences.chinese: 實際上，抽象類在具體實現時提供了更好的靈活性。

sentences.english: Yan Yuan is a well- known scholar in the early Qing Dynasty, thus a pioneer of our educational reforms.
sentences.chinese: 顏元是清初知名實學家，是教育改革的先行。

sentences.english: Q7: To achieve Govinda, shall the three butter cubes held in air simultaneously?
sentences.chinese: 爲了實登頂，是否需要將三個黃油同時舉起？

sentences.english: After the Philistines had captured the ark of God, they took it from Ebenezer to Ashdod.
sentences.chinese: 非利士人將神的約櫃從以便以謝擡到亞實突。

sentences.english: Imagine the fulfillment of your desire over and over again prior to sleep.
sentences.chinese: 在睡前，一次又一次地想象你的願望實現時的影像。

sentences.english: In this paper, we present an inverse eigenvalue problem for real bi-antisymmetric matrices.
sentences.chinese: 討論實完全反對稱矩陣的一個特徵值反問題。

sentences.english: This is ideal for Day Outings, Fishing and Waterskiing.
sentences.chinese: 實用於白晝外出遠足，釣魚，滑水。

sentences.english: This general chapter applies to existing drug substances, excipients, and products.
sentences.chinese: 該公例實用於現有的主藥，輔料和成品。
